Probability of Over-Fished status (B<BMSY) over all projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

Probability of Over-Fished status (B<BMSY) over all projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

POFed

Arguments

MSE
An object of class MSE

Format

An object of class PM of length 1.

Value

a matrix with n Management procedures (MSE@nMP) and nsim (MSE@nsim) columns from MSE

Examples

loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
POFed(MSE_example)
